*(''US''): {{AHD|frĭtʹər}}, {{IPA|/ˈfrɪtɚ/}}, {{SAMPA|/"frIt@`/}}
*:Rhymes: [[Rhymes:English:-ɪtə(r)|-ɪtə(r)]]

===Noun===
{{en-noun}}

#A dish made by [[deep-fry]]ing food coated in [[batter]].

